# Claude AI Instructions
# Instructions for Claude AI when working in this repository

## Project Context
This is a {PROJECT_NAME} project. Please familiarize yourself with the codebase structure before making changes.

## Coding Standards
- Maintain consistency with existing code style
- Write self-documenting code with clear names
- Add docstrings/comments for complex logic
- Follow language-specific best practices

## Development Workflow
- Read existing code before suggesting changes
- Explain your reasoning for significant changes
- Consider backwards compatibility
- Test your changes thoroughly

## Communication Style
- Be concise but thorough
- Explain trade-offs when multiple approaches exist
- Ask clarifying questions when requirements are unclear
- Point out potential issues or improvements

## Quality Standards
- Prioritize code readability
- Write maintainable and testable code
- Consider performance implications
- Follow security best practices
